        "action": "Create a legal right & formal process to renounce ILR & Settled Status",
        "additional_details": "We believe that ILR / Settled Status holders should have the legal right to decide whether they want to keep or renounce their ILR / Settled Status and to create a formal process for renunciation.",
        "background": "We want Parliament to pass a law which gives ILR / Settled Status the legal right to renounce their status.",
